API Endpoints (Examples)
- POST /projects/{projectId}/decisions
  - Body: { templateId?, fromScratch: boolean, draftMeta }
  - Response: { decisionId, status }
- GET /projects/{projectId}/decisions/{decisionId}
- PUT /projects/{projectId}/decisions/{decisionId}
- POST /projects/{projectId}/decisions/{decisionId}/publish
