- PUT /projects/{projectId}/decisions/{decisionId}/options/{optionId}
- POST /files/upload
- GET /files/{fileId}
- GET /templates
- POST /projects/{projectId}/decisions/{decisionId}/audit

Security
- Authentication: JWT/OAuth per project context
- Authorization: Role-based access control (project editors can create/edit; clients can view/publish only via link if permitted)
- Public links: Shared client links with token-based access; revocable by project owner
- Audit: All create/update/delete/publish actions must be logged

Validation
- Frontend: live validation with inline messages; steps blocked if invalid
- Backend: server-side validation mirroring frontend rules; precise error messages

Performance & Reliability
- Incremental saves: autosave draft after each step
- File uploads: resumable uploads; progress indicators; server-side chunk handling if needed
- Loading states: Global Loading Page for long tasks (export, large uploads)
- Retry mechanisms on transient failures

